          <figure class="image is-16by9">
            <img src="{{ projects.colors_of_the_night.image }}" alt="Colors Of The Night">
          </figure>
        </div>

        <div class="card-content">
          <h3 class="has-text-light">Colors Of The Night</h3>

          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag is-dark">Composition</span>
          </div>

          <p><i>Colors Of The Night</i> is my second EP that released in July 2019. It features four nighttime stories told in beautiful music.</p>

          <div class="buttons">
