            <img src="{{ projects.blue_moon.image }}" alt="Blue Moon">
          </figure>
        </div>

        <div class="card-content">
          <h3 class="has-text-light">Blue Moon</h3 data-tag-collapse data-tags="composition">

          <div class="tags">
            <span class="tag is-dark">Composition</span>
          </div>

          <p><i>Blue Moon</i> is a collection of four tracks that tell a story about the difference between fantasy and reality. This EP released on major streaming platforms in March 2018.</p>

